# Bookmark Manager

This is a simple Bookmark Manager using Bash scripts, Git, and Docker. It allows you to add, view, and search bookmarks using the following scripts:

## Scripts
- `add_bookmark.sh`: Adds a bookmark (URL & Title).
- `view_bookmarks.sh`: Displays all saved bookmarks.
- `search_bookmark.sh`: Searches bookmarks by keyword.

## Git & GitHub
This project uses Git for version control and is available on [GitHub](https://github.com/your-username/bookmark-manager).

## Docker
The project includes a Docker setup to persist the bookmarks. Run the following commands to build and start the container:

1. `docker-compose build`
2. `docker-compose up`
